title: Regret or Hard Work
itunes:title: Regret or Hard Work
description:
Ep 123 - "The only thing worse than the pain of hard work is the pain of regret" In this episode I talk about how the seeds you plant today will become the life that you live in the future. My hope for you is that you will be able to work hard for what you believe in today in order to create the life of your dreams tomorrow.
